        <heading>Section </heading>
        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 4.  APPOINTMENT OF COUNSEL
Art. 957.  Appointment of counsel
The juvenile court or traffic referee may appoint an attorney to represent the child whenever appointment of counsel is required in the interests of justice.</p>
        </content>
